      "step_title": "Overview",
      "content": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 26); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">This guide introduces you to QPOS sales reports, explaining what they are and how they can help you make smart business decisions. You&#39;ll learn about the different types of reports available in your BackOffice.</span></p>",
