      "step_title": "Before You Begin",
      "content": "<ul><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Access to your QPOS BackOffice.</span></li></ul><p></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">A computer or tablet with internet access.</span></li></ul>",
